---
title: Sticky Chinese Pork & Eggplant with Garlic Rice & Pickled Onion
description: When this dish was brought to our test kitchen table, it disappeared in record time! With a delicious combination of baby
broccoli, tender eggplant, toasted sesame seeds and pork with mild Sichuan garlic paste, it's sure to be a hit at your table too.
